Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Question}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.40,0:00:02.77,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Good day!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.44,0:00:07.61,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I, Lilie, will be presenting \N today’s PokéProblem!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.61,0:00:12.74,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Which Pokémon awakens today?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.74,0:00:15.50,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Get the answer at the end of the episode!
Comment: 10,0:00:15.50,0:00:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.29,0:00:20.17,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Breakfast time!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.17,0:00:25.17,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Satoshi and the others have \N made it through the Alola Pokémon League.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.17,0:00:28.17,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,It’s been a while since they’ve \N had breakfast at home...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.97,0:00:34.81,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Data on how Melmetal ingests food... \N Updated-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.02,0:00:39.52,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,It’s Stockpiling at \N an impressive rate, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.52,0:00:42.19,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,I love big families!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.61,0:00:46.19,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Agoyon?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.91,0:00:54.24,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It’s an Ultra Hole-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.96,0:01:01.29,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Agoyon...
Comment: 10,0:01:03.46,0:01:03.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Comment: 10,0:02:31.51,0:02:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.69,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You’re leaving, huh, Agoyon?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.23,0:02:50.61,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.11,0:02:57.74,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,In your world, there’s all those Bebenom \N waiting for you to come back, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.33,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Agoyon.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.33,0:03:08.71,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to help Alola... \N For coming to help us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.38,0:03:13.97,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Your 100,000 Volts was the coolest!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.01,Main,Burnet,0,0,0,,Let’s meet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.01,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Say hi to the Bebenom for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.68,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Oh, and the Radiant One, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.60,0:03:26.27,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right, Pikachu! \N Let’s send Agoyon off with a 100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.65,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,100,000 Volts!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.20,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.21,0:03:56.47,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,All right. Now, don’t forget \N what you just learned!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.01,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.10,0:04:06.98,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,By the way, how do you guys plan to \N spend the upcoming vacation?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.98,0:04:09.35,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Me! Me, me, me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.81,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Man, you’re {\i1}really{\i0} excited, Māmane.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.19,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,I’m going to Tokusane City \N with Big Mu{honorific note: Mu-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.49,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Tokusane City?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.03,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,In the Hoenn Region?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.03,0:04:18.91,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.91,0:04:21.62,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,I’ve been dying to go see \N the Tokusane Space Center!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.62,0:04:24.12,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,The Space Center? You mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.12,0:04:29.25,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,That’s right! \N I want to be an astronaut!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.58,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.50,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Your dream is so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.96,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,W-Well... Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.17,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,So I’m starting with \N what I can do now.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.59,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,It’s your first step \N towards your dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.34,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Just a small step, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.34,0:04:44.01,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,No, it’s a giant leap!{This line wrote itself. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.77,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.77,0:04:48.48,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,So, Kaki, what are {\i1}you{\i0} gonna do \N during vacation?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.27,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.19,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,...will battle Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.15,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.24,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,We didn’t get to face off \N in the League, after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.24,0:05:01.24,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I want one more chance \N to have an all-out battle with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.87,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Sure! You’re on!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.41,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I won’t lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.41,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Right back at you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.66,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I will win!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.00,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,No, I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.33,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,They’re at it again...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.79,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.79,0:05:15.17,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,All right, that’s enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.09,0:05:19.22,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I look forward to hearing \N the results of your battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.51,Main,Satoshi & Kaki,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.51,0:05:23.18,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,So, what are your plans, Suiren?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.85,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,I’m helping Dad with \N his ocean survey.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.56,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,What are you surveying?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.85,0:05:29.73,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Believe it or not...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.14,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,It’s Manaphy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.23,Main,Mao & Mamane,0,0,0,,Manaphy?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.23,0:05:36.07,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,That’ll be invaluable data-roto! \N I hope you’ll let me record it-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.36,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Manaphy. Seafaring Pokémon. \N Water type.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.70,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Born on a cold seafloor,{This dex entry is a combination of its Pearl and Platinum entries. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.70,0:05:49.12,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,it possesses a wondrous power that lets it \N bond with any kind of Pokémon.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.29,0:05:56.25,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’m going to give Aina Cafeteria \N a little bit of a makeover!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.71,0:06:01.34,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I want to make it into a restaurant that not just humans, \N but also Pokémon can enjoy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.01,0:06:08.39,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Before that, I’m holding a tasting party for \N the new Pokémon dishes, so please come, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.81,0:06:15.06,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I really want to awaken Magearna!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.06,0:06:18.69,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I will give that goal my full power \N over the vacation!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.32,0:06:21.86,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You’re all awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.32,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, \N other than battling Kaki?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.20,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.74,0:06:31.04,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, \N I haven’t really thought about it...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.93,0:06:48.89,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.14,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.52,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Satoshi was {\i1}thinking{\i0}-roto?!{LMAO -Puto}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.52,0:06:55.48,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It’s not {\i1}that{\i0} shocking!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.85,0:06:59.32,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You know, we’ve finished \N the Island Pilgrimage...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.90,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’m not sure what to do now.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.44,0:07:05.45,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Catch more Pokémon, maybe?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.37,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,What do you think, Professor?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.37,0:07:09.45,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.58,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,...you’ll have to \N figure it out yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.88,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,It should be easy for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.38,0:07:23.13,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,You’re the Alola Pokémon League \N Champion, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.64,0:07:30.18,Main,Kukui,0,0,0,,Well, you can take your time.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.85,0:07:31.76,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Right... {Suggesting "Yeah..." in place of "Right..."}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.61,0:07:42.90,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Have a look! \N That’s the Space Center!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.99,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,I’m so excited!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.29,Main,Suiren's Dad,0,0,0,,Manaphy is really quick.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.42,Main,Hou,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.83,Main,Sui,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.83,0:08:01.42,Main,Hou & Sui,0,0,0,,You’re gonna catch Manaphy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.42,0:08:03.59,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,That’s right. In order to research it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.59,0:08:05.34,Main,Hou & Sui,0,0,0,,Ama-mazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.72,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Ta-dough!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.09,0:08:15.73,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Welcome to the unveiling of \N Aina Cafeteria’s first-ever Pokémon menu items!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.85,0:08:22.06,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I made Fluffy Radish with different toppings \N to suit everyone’s tastes!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.07,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.70,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,They’re chowing down like mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.12,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,What an appetite!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.76,0:08:53.30,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’m so glad they all seem to like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.30,0:08:57.35,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Yes! It’s amazing that you made food \N that so perfectly appeals to everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.35,0:09:01.73,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Whenever I think back to that time \N I helped out in Master’s café...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.73,0:09:05.57,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Somehow, new Pokémon menu items \N just keep popping into my mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.57,0:09:10.40,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,People, Pokémon... \N All of Aina Cafeteria’s customers...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.62,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I want to make dishes \N that’ll make them all smile!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.66,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,That’s right, Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.66,0:09:21.54,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Ms. Lychee{honorific note: Lychee-san} is going to be \N the referee for our battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.58,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Ms. Lychee{honorific note: Lychee-san}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.58,0:09:25.46,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I met her the other day \N and told her about our battle,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.71,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,and she was all in on it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.71,0:09:31.30,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,And she said she could do it {\i1}tomorrow,{\i0} even! \N No need to wait for vacation!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.34,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.05,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right! Let’s do it then! \N I’m all in!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.14,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.06,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.93,0:09:41.23,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, how are things with Magearna?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.02,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.82,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I tried quite a few things...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.82,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,But nothing worked...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.62,0:09:59.37,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Don’t worry! \N I’m sure you can do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.46,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Satoshi is right!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.46,0:10:06.79,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,You’re always watching Pokémon carefully \N and trying to understand them!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.79,0:10:10.51,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,I’m sure your feelings will get through \N sooner or later!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.22,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.76,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.06,0:10:22.89,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,The Soul Heart is the key...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.73,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Father kept on trying to...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.99,0:11:21.87,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Oh, dear... \N I must have fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.42,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Zoroark...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.34,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Fire Punch!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.55,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Accel Rock!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.06,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Stone Edge!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.98,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Dodge and use Turning Swallow Strike!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.28,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Bite attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.29,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Use Slash!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.43,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Lugarugan!
Comment: 10,0:12:29.48,0:12:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.27,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll get Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.90,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Lugarugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.49,0:12:44.62,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Let’s finish this, Lizardon!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.13,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,My full body...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.13,0:12:52.46,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,...soul...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.46,0:12:53.96,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,...and power!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.13,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,The zenith of all that I am...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.13,0:13:00.76,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Become a blazing flame that burns \N like the mountain of Akala!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.80,0:13:05.18,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,This is our...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.31,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,...full power!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.90,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Radial Edgestorm!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.57,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Dynamic...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.49,0:13:23.99,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,...Full Flame!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.06,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Stand up, Lizardon!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.19,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Lugarugan, can you still stand?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.61,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,Both are unable to—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.86,0:14:00.90,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Lugarugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.95,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,Lizardon is unable to battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.08,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,As such, the winner is Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.42,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lugarugan!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.51,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,That was an awesome battle-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.68,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.47,0:14:32.89,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Lizardon, you fought well. \N Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.11,0:14:41.61,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Satoshi, that was a great battle!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.78,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.12,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I used my full power! \N I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.33,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,Satoshi... Kaki...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.83,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,You were just the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.84,0:15:03.51,Main,Satoshi & Kaki,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.14,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,So, what next?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.52,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.52,0:15:16.98,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,How do the two of you plan on \N becoming stronger in the future?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.77,0:15:21.57,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’m... not really sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.65,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Professor Kukui said \N I should figure it out for myself...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.53,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I have plenty of stuff I want to do!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.16,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I’ll continue my Island Pilgrimage!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.16,0:15:35.04,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I want to challenge Mr. Hala{honorific note: Hala-san}, Mr. Kuchinashi{honorific note: Kuchinashi-san}, \N and Hāpu'u{honorific note: Hāpu'u-san}’s Grand Trials!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.54,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I want to master more types of Z-Moves!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.54,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,And I’ll become much, much stronger!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.92,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,All for the sake of \N protecting the flames of Wela!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.80,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Just like Grandfather did!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.22,0:15:50.43,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,Was that a declaration that \N you’ll become the Island King?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.85,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Kaki’s dream is to \N be the Island King-roto?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.85,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,That’s perfect for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.85,0:15:58.31,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.31,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.90,0:16:05.44,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,If so, then you’ll have to learn about \N the outside world, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.07,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,The outside... world?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.07,0:16:11.33,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,It’s important to know of \N the outside world.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.33,0:16:14.70,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,Changing your surroundings \N broadens your perspective.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.70,0:16:19.54,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,It allows you to calmly look back and \N reconsider the person you’d been until then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.71,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,Isn’t that right, Satoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.29,0:16:27.17,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,You understand, \N since you’ve been training in Alola, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.10,0:16:36.98,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Lilie...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.23,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Lilie.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.65,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.98,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,I was really surprised...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.82,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,...when James contacted me \N out of the blue.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.53,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry for the short notice.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.53,0:16:53.66,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I wanted to let Zoroark \N meet Magearna.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.79,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Zoroark?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.37,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.58,0:17:04.29,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Zoroark must have been watching \N Father’s research right by his side.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.92,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.30,0:17:10.97,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I was thinking about that, \N and then it hit me that Magearna and Zoroark...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.97,0:17:13.97,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,...would love to be reunited, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.18,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Figures {\i1}you’d{\i0} think of that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.31,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Zoroark!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.74,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Look, Magearna. It’s Zoroark!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.62,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,You recognize it, don’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.75,0:17:41.79,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Zoroark!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.50,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Look! It’s Magearna!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.22,0:17:55.64,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I knew it’d remember!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.64,0:17:56.43,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.07,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.99,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,This is Zoroark’s illusion.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.95,0:18:23.04,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,You called, Princess Lilie?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.63,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.24,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,I didn’t know you were \N such a tomboy.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.83,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I was still a baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.25,0:19:07.92,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,Lilie, I hope you and Magearna \N will be good friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.63,0:19:14.72,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,Magearna. \N Once you can move again,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.55,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,look after Lilie for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.76,0:19:22.85,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,Please protect my little princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.44,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,We’re home!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.15,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,We’re back.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.36,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Lilie!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.91,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,You’re standing up!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.95,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Mohn, when?! \N When did she learn to stand?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.66,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,Just now. \N It was just a few seconds ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.66,0:19:46.50,Main,Lusamine,0,0,0,,Oh, I missed \N a priceless moment!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.71,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Good work, Lilie!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.75,Main,Mohn,0,0,0,,Such a good girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.59,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.63,0:19:56.76,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I want to see you...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.55,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.47,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Magearna...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.05,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,You’re...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.51,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,...awake?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.80,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,At last!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.81,0:20:48.60,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I’m so happy, Magearna!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.16,0:21:10.75,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,It’s important to know of \N the outside world.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.75,0:21:13.88,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,Changing your surroundings \N broadens your perspective.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.88,0:21:18.80,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,It allows you to calmly look back and \N reconsider the person you’d been until then.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.63,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,Isn’t that right, Satoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.72,0:21:27.22,Main,Lychee,0,0,0,,You understand, \N since you’ve been training in Alola, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.23,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ve decided!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.86,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I want to see the rest of the world!{“Which is most definitely not a thing I’ve ever done before!” -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.61,0:21:41.36,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Pikachu, let’s go back to Masara Town.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.49,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’m sure there’s so much more \N awesome stuff to see in the world!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.12,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,There’s gotta be loads more \N Pokémon out there!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.29,0:21:53.58,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Satoshi has chosen his own path.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.58,0:21:57.84,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Where will that path \N take him?
Comment: 10,0:21:59.46,0:21:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 10,0:23:20.46,0:23:20.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Answer}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.30,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.30,0:23:28.55,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,The Pokémon who woke up today \N was Magearna!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.97,0:23:31.64,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,At last, Magearna is awake!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.64,0:23:37.02,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,It’s all thanks to Zoroark \N showing me its memories of Father!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.65,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Zoroark!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.78,0:23:46.91,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,How does the fresh air feel, \N Magearna?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.12,0:23:56.25,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?!
Comment: 10,0:24:00.50,0:24:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.88,0:24:03.34,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Satoshi is late...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.34,0:24:06.09,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,It’s kinda quiet without him, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.09,0:24:09.39,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,He’s always burning hot \N at full power, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.39,0:24:10.89,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,He’s loud, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.89,0:24:12.35,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Especially while battling.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.35,0:24:14.85,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,That’s why it’s kinda quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.85,0:24:18.48,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Next time, on Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.48,0:24:21.69,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Thank you, Alola! \N The Start of New Journeys!!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.69,0:24:26.03,Main,Them,0,0,0,,{\i1}Won’t Satoshi be here soon?{\i0}
