Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.54,0:01:07.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:07.96,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}{\fad(300,0)}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.96,0:01:14.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:14.26,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}{\fad(0,300)}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.89,0:01:25.61,OP,,0,0,0,,You’ve gotten a lot tanner since we first met
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:25.61,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}You’ve gotten a lot tanner since we first met
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.61,0:01:31.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2.25}And your clothes are a bit dirtier, but that’s the best look for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:31.36,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2.25}{\be3\bord9}And your clothes are a bit dirtier, but that’s the best look for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.36,0:01:35.87,OP,,0,0,0,,Look, the tears of frustration you’ve hidden beneath your cap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:35.87,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Look, the tears of frustration you’ve hidden beneath your cap
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.87,0:01:41.12,OP,,0,0,0,,will be dried up by the sun in no time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:41.12,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}will be dried up by the sun in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.46,OP,,0,0,0,,Learning until you’re all worn out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.46,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Learning until you’re all worn out,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.46,0:01:45.54,OP,,0,0,0,,playing until nightfall,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:45.54,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}playing until nightfall,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.55,OP,,0,0,0,,go on, chase after the Rainbow Feather
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.55,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}go on, chase after the Rainbow Feather
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.76,OP,,0,0,0,,You were the one who taught us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:54.76,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}You were the one who taught us
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.76,0:01:59.64,OP,,0,0,0,,how important it is to speak our dreams out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:59.64,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}how important it is to speak our dreams out loud
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.64,0:02:04.06,OP,,0,0,0,,Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:04.06,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Don’t fear things you’ve never seen or done
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.06,0:02:09.94,OP,,0,0,0,,Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:09.94,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Now run, future hero, and feel the Tailwind at your back!
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.94,0:02:13.82,OP,,0,0,0,,Never forget your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:13.82,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Never forget your dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.82,0:02:18.91,OP,,0,0,0,,With your backpack full of stuff, you’re ready to go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:18.91,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}With your backpack full of stuff, you’re ready to go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.91,0:02:23.92,OP,,0,0,0,,It’s your adventure which nobody else can picture
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:23.92,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}It’s your adventure which nobody else can picture
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.92,0:02:31.51,OP,,0,0,0,,Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:31.51,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{\be3\bord9}Step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:31.51,OPp2,,0,0,0,,{=3}
Comment: 10,0:21:59.46,0:21:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{=4}ENDING
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.65,0:22:15.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}How long has it been
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:15.27,EDp2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}How long has it been
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.27,0:22:18.32,ED,,0,0,0,,since I bid Masara Town farewell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:18.32,EDp2,,0,0,0,,since I bid Masara Town farewell?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.40,ED,,0,0,0,,Got so many cuts, scratches, and friends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.40,EDp2,,0,0,0,,Got so many cuts, scratches, and friends
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.40,0:22:24.53,ED,,0,0,0,,I’m kinda proud of that
